                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10263" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1537</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">841 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">借 “数据” 之力，扬 “海科” 之帆 ：中远海科数据资产入表实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Leveraging Data Power, Charting the Course for COSCO Shipping Technology: Exploratory Practice of Data Asset Recognition in Financial Statements</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钟廷勇，彭丽，何欣仪，邹镕蔚</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中远海运科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">航运科技；会计确认与计量；数据资产；数据治理；价值创造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shipping Technology; Accounting Recognition and measurement; Data Assets; Data Governance; Value Creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在数字经济时代，数据资产化正成为重塑企业竞争格局的核心动能。中远海科作为航运科技领域的领军企业，凭借深厚的技术积累和敏锐的市场洞察力，在数据资产化浪潮中勇立潮头。本案例重点描述了中远海科在数据资产入表方面的实践历程，涵盖其数据治理架构的搭建、数据资产的确认与计量方法、数据治理的多维度努力，以及数据资产入表后所创造的价值。在政策推动与市场需求的双重驱动下，中远海科通过成立专业团队、建立数据治理制度与平台等举措，成功实现了数据资产的规范化管理与入表，为行业提供了可借鉴的范例。案例旨在帮助学生理解数据资产定义、类型、确认、计量及治理等关键内容，启发学生思考数据资产入表带来的价值，为航运企业提供数据资产入表经验，也为其他行业实现数据价值提供有益借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Leveraging Data Power, Charting the Course for COSCO Shipping Technology: Exploratory Practice of Data Asset Recognition in Financial Statements
Abstract:In the era of digital economy, the assetization of data is becoming the core driving force for reshaping the competitive landscape of enterprises. COSCO Shipping Technology, as a leading enterprise in the field of shipping technology, has taken the lead in the wave of data assetization by leveraging its profound technological accumulation and acute market insight. This case study focuses on the practical journey of COSCO Shipping Technology in the process of listing data assets, covering the establishment of its data governance framework, the methods for confirming and measuring data assets, its multi-dimensional efforts in data governance, and the value created after listing data assets. Driven by both policy promotion and market demand, COSCO Shipping Technology has successfully achieved standardized management and listing of data assets through measures such as establishing a professional team, setting up data governance systems and platforms, providing a reference model for the industry. The case aims to help students understand key aspects such as the definition, types, confirmation, measurement, and governance of data assets, inspire students to think about the value brought by listing data assets, offer experience in listing data assets to shipping enterprises, and provide beneficial references for other industries to realize the value of data.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《高级财务会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数据资产含义、分类和特征；数据资产确认、计量的要点、难点及解决途径；数据治理及其体系构建、数据资产入表价值等内容</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
